      <title>欧洲面临艰难抉择，或面临几乎零增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/europe-has-choice-of-doing-hard-work-or-facing-next-to-no-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界大型企业联合会表示，除非欧洲领导人开始进行改革并为大幅增加私人投资创造条件，否则欧洲将面临严峻的经济前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/europe-has-choice-of-doing-hard-work-or-facing-next-to-no-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
